# Payment Pages (SwiftPay Builder)

Module: `/payment-pages` and create-page wizard. Defines page shell, steps, and builder layout (not individual UI components).

## Dashboard (`/payment-pages`)
- Standard page pattern: `px-[32px] pt-[12px] pb-[32px] bg-white min-h-full`
- Action bar: "Create Page" Primary CTA (High emphasis, `Plus` icon) + search + filters
- Table: `grid-cols-[1.5fr_1.5fr_1fr_0.8fr_0.8fr_0.4fr]`, without vertical separators
- Status chips: Active `text-[#21c179] bg-[#e3f6ec]`, Expired `text-[#fd5154] bg-[#ffebef]`, Draft `text-[#7e7e7e] bg-[#fafafa]`
- Actions: kebab menu (Share, Download QR, Edit, Expire/Reactivate, Delete)

## Create Page Entry
- Popup (`type="form"`) with 4 option cards
- Each card: `border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[12px] p-5 hover:bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Icon: `size-10 rounded-[8px] bg-[#e0f5fd]`

## Step Wizard
- Component spec and tokens: **`.cursor/rules/components/step-wizard.mdc`**
- Used on all three wizard screens: `PageInfoForm`, `PageBuilder`, `AdditionalSettings`

## Wizard footer (`PageLevelMenu`)
- Shared sticky footer on **Step 1–3** — see **`.cursor/rules/components/page-level-menu.mdc`**

## Step 1: Page Information (`PageInfoForm.tsx`)
- **Spacing:** No extra top padding on the main content wrapper (`pt-0`); vertical gap after the step card comes from `StepWizard`’s nav `pb-5` only. Content **left-aligned** in the frame (`justify-start`, same `px-[32px]` as the wizard)
- **No card** around fields: **two-column grid** is `w-full` edge-to-edge within horizontal padding (`grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2`, **`gap-x-6`** = **24px** horizontal gap between columns, `gap-y-5` vertical)
- Row pairing: Form Name | HTML Title; **URL Path** full width (`md:col-span-2`); Support Contact | Support Email; Freeze Date (single cell in last row)
- Header: title + single subtitle line (`text-[#7e7e7e]`)
- All inputs use `TextField` (floating-label, 56px, `rounded-[4px]`); wrap each field in `min-w-0` for grid overflow
- Actions: **`PageLevelMenu`** — Cancel + Continue to Page Builder (`primaryDisabled` until required fields valid); no Clear all
- Cover Image has moved to Step 2

## Step 2: Page Builder

### Two frames
1. **Frame 1 — StepWizard**: identical to other steps (no changes).
2. **Frame 2 — Builder workspace**: fills remaining height; divided into **page tabs bar** + **three-panel** layout.

### Browser-style page tabs (`PageTabsBar.tsx`)
- End-to-end `border-b border-[#e0e0e0] bg-[#fafafa]`, sits above the three panels
- Each tab: `rounded-t-[8px]`, active tab `bg-white border-x border-t -mb-px` (overlaps bottom border); inactive transparent, hover `bg-[#f0f0f0]`
- **Delete**: `X` icon per tab (hidden until hover), disabled when only 1 page
- **Rename**: double-click tab title to edit inline
- **Add Page**: `Plus` icon + "Add Page" text, right of tabs

### Three-panel layout
- **Left — Component Palette** (`ComponentPalette.tsx`, `w-[280px]`):
  - Toggle bar: **All Components** | **Used (N)** — underline active `border-b-2 border-[#004299]`
  - **All Components**: categorised draggable components (Display, Layout, Input, Choices, Date, Pricing, Verification, Address, eCommerce, Other)
  - **Used**: ordered list of components on active page (with grip icon + label + order #); empty state "No components added yet"
  - Drag from All onto canvas (HTML5 Drag and Drop, no external dependency)

- **Center — Canvas** (`BuilderCanvas.tsx`, `flex-1`):
  - `bg-[#fafafa]`, zoom toolbar (pinch / ⌃+scroll, **−/+** buttons, **Reset**; 50%–200%)
  - Canvas width adapts to **preview mode**: `max-w-[600px]` (web) or `max-w-[375px]` (mobile)
  - Drop zone `border-[#004299] bg-[#f5f9fe]`, selected `border-[#004299]`
  - Input previews: `h-[56px] border border-[#e0e0e0] rounded-[4px]` floating-label style
  - Cover Image (drag-and-drop upload, PNG/JPG up to 5MB)

- **Right — Property Panel** (`PropertyPanel.tsx`, `w-[320px]`):
  - **Preview toggle**: Web (Monitor icon) / Mobile (Smartphone icon) — pill switch, active `bg-[#004299] text-white`; controls canvas `max-w` above
  - **Component properties**: shown when component selected — type badge, Label, Placeholder, Required, Show, Toggles (Disable/Help/Analytics/Multi), Options list (dropdown/radio/checkbox), **Rules & Validation** (min/max length, regex)
  - **Empty state**: "Select a component on the canvas to edit its properties and rules."

- **Bottom bar**: `PageLevelMenu` — Clear all (disabled when nothing to clear) + Back to Page Info + Save & Continue; see `components/page-level-menu.mdc`

## Step 3: Additional Settings
- Primary tabs: Post Transaction | Notifications
- Post Transaction: Redirect URL, Success Message
- Notifications: SMS toggle + text, Email toggle + subject + body
- **Footer**: `PageLevelMenu` with `primaryEmphasis="success"` — Back to Builder + Save & Publish (`bg-[#21c179]`); no Clear all
